<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" ?><?xml-stylesheet type="text/xsl" href="..\config8\suzuki.xsl" ?><!DOCTYPE suzuki [<!ENTITY % sdatacharaents SYSTEM "..\config8\sdatacharaents.txt">%sdatacharaents;]><suzuki><manual>
<section sectnbr = "5A">
<servcat sctnbr = "05" scnbr = "01">
<configtype typenbr = "0">
<servinfotype sitcode = "6">
<servinfo servinfosgmlid = "AENAP70B5106052" svcinfotypenbr = "08" svcinfoqualnbr = "02" page = "2" supplyoff = "1" modify = "0">
<title>
Transaxle Rear Cover (O/D and 2nd Coast Brake Piston) Assembly Disassembly and Reassembly
</title>
<ptxt>
<intxrefpoff refid = "AENAP70B5106037">A/T Assembly Disassembly</intxrefpoff>
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
<intxrefpoff refid = "AENAP70B5106064">A/T Assembly Reassembly</intxrefpoff>
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
<intxrefpoff refid = "AENAP70B5106051">Transaxle Rear Cover (O/D and 2nd Coast Brake Piston) Assembly Components</intxrefpoff>
</ptxt>
<servinfosub id = "AENAP70B5106052001">
<title>
Disassembly
</title>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Using special tools and hydraulic press, compress O/D and 2nd coast brake return spring subassembly, then remove snap ring.
</ptxt>
<servicetool>
<servicetoolitem id = "L5A028">
<s-part>
(A)
</s-part>
<s-number num = "09926-96030">
09926–96030
</s-number>
</servicetoolitem>
<servicetoolitem id = "L5A029">
<s-part>
(B)
</s-part>
<s-number num = "09946-06710">
09946–06710
</s-number>
</servicetoolitem>
</servicetool>
<attention2>
<ptxt>
Do not press in O/D and 2nd coast brake return spring subassembly more than 1 mm (0.04 in.).
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
Excessive compression may cause damage to O/D and 2nd coast brake return spring subassembly and/or piston.
</ptxt>
</attention2>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Remove O/D and 2nd coast brake return spring subassembly.
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I7V10A510079.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "45.539mm" ver = "01" gw = "127" gh = "112"/>
<callout>
<table frame = "all" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<tgroup cols = "2" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<colspec colnum = "1" colname = "1" colwidth = "0.315in"/>
<colspec colnum = "2" colname = "2" colwidth = "1.353in"/>
<tbody>
<row rowsep = "0">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" align = "right">
<ptxt>
1.
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
Transaxle rear cover
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
</callout>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Apply compressed air (400 – 800 kPa, 4.1 – 8.2 kgf/cm<sup>2</sup>, 58.0 – 116 psi) to oil hole (2) of transaxle rear cover (1) to remove O/D and 2nd coast brake piston.
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I2RH0B510202.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "50.619mm" ver = "01" gw = "192" gh = "126"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<c-change/>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Remove O/D and 2nd coast brake piston front O-ring (1) and rear O-ring (2) from O/D and 2nd coast brake piston.
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I2RH0B510203.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "46.005mm" ver = "01" gw = "187" gh = "113"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Remove rear cover seal rings (1) from rear cover.
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I2RH0B510204.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "48.672mm" ver = "01" gw = "187" gh = "121"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Remove rear cover plugs (1) from rear cover.
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I2RH0B510205.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "52.101mm" ver = "01" gw = "135" gh = "131"/>
</figure>
</s1>
</servinfosub>
<c-change/>
<servinfosub id = "AENAP70B5106052002">
<title>
Reassembly
</title>
<ptxt>
<intxrefpoff refid = "AENAP70B5106053">Transaxle Rear Cover (O/D and 2nd Coast Brake Piston) Assembly Inspection</intxrefpoff>
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
Reverse disassembly procedure noting the following points.
</ptxt>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Use new seal rings and O-rings. Apply ATF to seal rings and O-rings before installation.
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Tighten rear cover plugs to specified torque. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENAP70B5106051"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
First, tighten seal ring to 5 mm (0.2 in.), then install seal ring.
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Do not open rear cover seal ring too wide to attach.
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I2RH0B510206.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "49.095mm" ver = "01" gw = "193" gh = "122"/>
<callout>
<table frame = "all" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<tgroup cols = "2" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<colspec colnum = "1" colname = "1" colwidth = "0.315in"/>
<colspec colnum = "2" colname = "2" colwidth = "1.388in"/>
<tbody>
<row rowsep = "0">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" align = "right">
<ptxt>
1.
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
Transaxle rear cover
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
</callout>
</figure>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Do not damage O/D and 2nd coast brake return spring subassembly and piston by pressing in O/D and 2nd coast brake return spring subassembly passing through its original installing position over 1 mm (0.04 in.).
</ptxt>
<servicetool>
<servicetoolitem id = "L5A030">
<s-part>
(A)
</s-part>
<s-number num = "09926-96030">
09926–96030
</s-number>
</servicetoolitem>
<servicetoolitem id = "L5A031">
<s-part>
(B)
</s-part>
<s-number num = "09946-06710">
09946–06710
</s-number>
</servicetoolitem>
</servicetool>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I7V10A510079.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "45.539mm" ver = "01" gw = "127" gh = "112"/>
<callout>
<table frame = "all" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<tgroup cols = "2" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<colspec colnum = "1" colname = "1" colwidth = "0.315in"/>
<colspec colnum = "2" colname = "2" colwidth = "1.405in"/>
<tbody>
<row rowsep = "0">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" align = "right">
<ptxt>
1.
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
Transaxle rear cover
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
</callout>
</figure>
</item>
</list1>
</servinfosub>
</servinfo>
</servinfotype>
</configtype>
</servcat>
</section></manual></suzuki>
